



Sir
Richmond Febry. 7th. 1781



Finding by your letter of the 30th. of December that the justice of Commissary Clarkes account of the deficiences in the issues [of] [551]provision to the Convention Troops is not acknowledged by you; be pleased to make me a return of those deficiences according to what you suppose to be right.
I am Sr. &c &c &c &c,

T.J.

